file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: API V1
  version: v1
paths:
  "/events.json":
    get:
      summary: list events
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
    post:
      summary: create event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
  "/events/new":
    get:
      summary: new event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
  "/events/{id}/edit.json":
    parameters:
    - name: id
      in: path
      description: id
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    get:
      summary: edit event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
  "/events/{id}.json":
    parameters:
    - name: id
      in: path
      description: id
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    get:
      summary: show event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
    patch:
      summary: update event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
    put:
      summary: update event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
    delete:
      summary: delete event
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful
servers:
- url: http://localhost:3000
